"><small>РСП</small> Искупать, искупление</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note14a\" data-full-marker=\"14а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123523123\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.29?lang=rus#p29\">Алма 20:29</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"16\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note16a\" data-full-marker=\"16а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123523124\" id=\"note16a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/22.1?lang=rus#p1\">Алма 22:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"17\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note17a\" data-full-marker=\"17а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123523125\" id=\"note17a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.44?lang=rus#p44\">У. и З. 18:44</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note22a\" data-full-marker=\"22а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123523126\" id=\"note22a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/134.1-4?lang=rus#p1\">У. и З. 134:1–4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.11?lang=rus#p11\">С. В. 1:11</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/free-freedom_liberty?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Свобода, свободный</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1а","pid":"123523091","context":"разделились","text":"<p data-aid=\"123523116\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.13,17?lang=rus#p13\">Алма 17:13, 17</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.13,17?lang=rus#p13","text":"Алма 17:13, 17"}]},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2а","pid":"123523092","c